(7, 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andorra', '', 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catalan_language', 0, '', '33.0', 2013, 'Andorra (/ænˈdɔrə/; Catalan pronunciation: [ənˈdorə], locally: [anˈdɔra]), officially the Principality of Andorra (Catalan: Principat d''Andorra), also called the Principality of the Valleys of Andorra (Catalan: Principat de les Valls d''Andorra), is a landlocked microstate in Southwestern Europe, located in the eastern Pyrenees mountains and bordered by Spain and France.', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andorra', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Andorra.svg', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Andorra.svg?width=300'),
(8, 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angola', '', 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language', 6484, '107', '148', 2013, 'Angola, officially the Republic of Angola (Portuguese: República de Angola pronounced: [ʁɛˈpublikɐ dɨ ɐ̃ˈɡɔlɐ]; Kikongo, Kimbundu, Umbundu: Repubilika ya Ngola), is a country in Southern Africa bordered by Namibia on the south, the Democratic Republic of the Congo on the north, and Zambia on the east; its west coast is on the Atlantic Ocean and Luanda is its capital city.', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angola', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Angola.svg', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Angola.svg?width=300'),
(9, 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antigua_and_Barbuda', '', 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/English_language', 18026, '', '60', 2011, 'Antigua and Barbuda ({{|æ|n|ˈ|t|iː|ɡ|ə|_|æ|n|d|_|b|ɑr|ˈ|b|juː|d|ə}}; Spanish for "ancient" and "bearded") is a twin-island nation lying between the Caribbean Sea and the Atlantic Ocean. It consists of two major inhabited islands, Antigua and Barbuda, and a number of smaller islands (including Great Bird, Green, Guinea, Long, Maiden and York Islands and further south, the island of Redonda).', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antigua_and_Barbuda', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Antigua_and_Barbuda.svg', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Antigua_and_Barbuda.svg?width=300'),
