(35, 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbados', '', 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/English_overseas_possessions', 25100, '', '38', 2013, 'Barbados (/bɑrˈbeɪdɒs/ or /bɑrˈbeɪdoʊs/) is a sovereign island country in the Lesser Antilles. It is 34 kilometres (21 mi) in length and up to 23 kilometres (14 mi) in width, covering an area of 432 square kilometres (167 sq mi).', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barbados', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Barbados.svg', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Barbados.svg?width=300'),
