(86, 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_African_Republic', '', 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sango_language', 800, '', '179', 2011, 'The Central African Republic (CAR; Sango: Ködörösêse tî Bêafrîka; French: République centrafricaine pronounced: [ʁepyblik sɑ̃tʁafʁikɛn], or Centrafrique [sɑ̃tʀafʁik]) is a landlocked country in Central Africa. It is bordered by Chad in the north, Sudan in the northeast, South Sudan in the east, the Democratic Republic of the Congo and the Republic of the Congo in the south and Cameroon in the west.', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Central_African_Republic', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_the_Central_African_Republic.svg', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_the_Central_African_Republic.svg?width=300'),
(87, 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad', '', '', 1865, '150', '183.0', 2011, 'Chad (Arabic: تشاد‎ Tšād; French: Tchad /ˈtʃæd/), officially the Republic of Chad, is a landlocked country in Central Africa. It is bordered by Libya to the north, Sudan to the east, the Central African Republic to the south, Cameroon and Nigeria to the southwest and Niger to the west.Chad is divided into multiple regions: a desert zone in the north, an arid Sahelian belt in the centre and a more fertile Sudanese savanna zone in the south.', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chad', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Chad.svg', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Chad.svg?width=300'),
(88, 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile', '', 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language', 20105, '55', '40', 2013, 'Chile (/ˈtʃileɪ/ or /ˈtʃɪli/), officially the Republic of Chile (Spanish: República de Chile, [reˈpuβlika ðe ˈtʃile] ), is a South American country occupying a long, narrow strip of land between the Andes mountains to the east and the Pacific Ocean to the west. It borders Peru to the north, Bolivia to the northeast, Argentina to the east, and the Drake Passage in the far south.', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chile', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Chile.svg', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Chile.svg?width=300'),
