(156, 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia', '', 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Regions_of_Ethiopia', 1300, '', '173.0', 2011, 'Ethiopia (/ˌiːθiˈoʊpiə/; Amharic: ኢትዮጵያ?</span>, ʾĪtyōṗṗyā, About this sound listen ), officially known as the Federal Democratic Republic of Ethiopia, is a country located in the Horn of Africa. It is bordered by Eritrea to the north and northeast, Djibouti and Somalia to the east, Sudan and South Sudan to the west, and Kenya to the south.', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ethiopia', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Ethiopia.svg', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Ethiopia.svg?width=300'),
