(229, 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel', '', 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hebrew_language', 35658, '', '16', 2013, 'Israel /ˈɪzreɪəl/, officially the State of Israel (Hebrew: מְדִינַת יִשְׂרָאֵל, Medīnat Yisrā''el, IPA: [mediˈnat jisʁaˈʔel] ; Arabic: دولة إِسرائيل‎, Dawlat Isrāʼīl, IPA: [dawlat ʔisraːˈʔiːl]), is a country in Western Asia, on the south-eastern shore of the Mediterranean Sea.', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Israel', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Israel.svg', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Israel.svg?width=300'),
