(360, 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nauru', '', 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nauruan_language', 0, '135', '', 0, 'Nauru (English /nɑːˈuːruː/ nah-OO-roo), officially the Republic of Nauru and formerly known as Pleasant Island, is an island country in Micronesia in the South Pacific. Its nearest neighbour is Banaba Island in Kiribati, 300 kilometres (186 mi) to the east.', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nauru', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Nauru.svg', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Nauru.svg?width=300'),
