(605, 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom', '', 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scots_language', 38309, '21.0', '26', 2013, 'The United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland, commonly known as the United Kingdom (UK) or Britain /ˈbrɪ.tən/, is a sovereign state located off the north-western coast of continental Europe. The country includes the island of Great Britain (a term sometimes also loosely applied to the whole state), the north-eastern part of the island of Ireland, and many smaller islands.', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_Kingdom', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_the_United_Kingdom.svg', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_the_United_Kingdom.svg?width=300'),
