(619, 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uruguay', 'peso uruguayo', 'http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language', 17466, '', '51.0', 2012, 'Uruguay /ˈjʊərəɡwaɪ/, officially the Oriental Republic of Uruguay or the Eastern Republic of Uruguay or the Republic East of the Uruguay (River) (Spanish: República Oriental del Uruguay, pronounced: [reˈpuβlika oɾjenˈtal del uɾuˈɣwaj]), is a country in the southeastern region of South America. It is bordered by Argentina to its west and Brazil to its north and east, with the Atlantic Ocean to the south and southeast.', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Uruguay', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Uruguay.svg', 'http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Flag_of_Uruguay.svg?width=300'),
